        <rdfs:comment>Specifies the type of floor being considered, which affects both the heating and the cooling loads. See Table 4A, pages T4A-27 and following, ACCA Manual J Eighth Edition.</rdfs:comment>
    </owl:DatatypeProperty>
    


    <!-- https://www.auto.tuwien.ac.at/downloads/thinkhome/ontology/BuildingOntology.owl#hasFloorCrawlSpaceIsSealedValue -->

