        <rdfs:range rdf:resource="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#boolean"/>
        <rdfs:comment>Specifies whether or not the crawl space wall associated with this floor is well sealed from the outdoor air, which affects both the heating and cooling loads. See Figure A5-5, page A5-8, and Figure A5-17 page A5-16, ACCA Manual J Eighth Edition.</rdfs:comment>
    </owl:DatatypeProperty>
    


    <!-- https://www.auto.tuwien.ac.at/downloads/thinkhome/ontology/BuildingOntology.owl#hasFloorCrawlSpaceWallUValue -->

