        <rdfs:comment>Specifies whether or not to use a higher heating temperature difference value in calculating the heating loss for a floor (25 degrees F higher value is used in formula if floor is radiant). See Figure A5-5, page A5-8, ACCA Manual J Eighth Edition.</rdfs:comment>
    </owl:DatatypeProperty>
    


