        <rdfs:comment>Specifies the effective wall color, which depends on the actual color and whether the location is industrial or rural. See page 26.36, 1989 ASHRAE Handbook, Fundamentals volume.</rdfs:comment>
    </owl:DatatypeProperty>
    


    <!-- https://www.auto.tuwien.ac.at/downloads/thinkhome/ontology/BuildingOntology.owl#hasWallGroupManualJValue -->

