        <rdfs:comment>A piece of equipment serving an air-loop. This is generalized to be able to contain any type of air loop equipment. The air loop equipment are ordered as they exist on the airloop. A blow-through system should have fan listed before the coils. A draw-through system should have the fan listed after the coils.</rdfs:comment>
    </owl:Class>
    


