                        <owl:onDataRange rdf:resource="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string"/>
                    </owl:Restriction>
                </owl:intersectionOf>
            </owl:Class>
        </rdfs:subClassOf>
        <rdfs:comment>Parameters required by RTS load calculation method, as described in pages 29.25 and following of the 2001 ASHRAE Handbook, Fundamentals volume. Ignore this element and all elements under it if you are not planning to use that method.</rdfs:comment>
